Simple site for a small group of people to share urls.

- looks up url titles
- automatically adds thumbnails for YouTube, Vimeo, and Flickr urls
- embeds Flash mp3 player for mp3 urls
- supports Gravatar

To set up run create_db.sh and edit configuration in ajax.cgi.

Auth file format:

bcrypted password,username,email

require 'rubygems'
require 'bcrypt'
puts BCrypt::Password.create('secret')

Required gems:

bcrypt-ruby builder csv hpricot sqlite3

See http://matthewm.boedicker.org/urlshare/ for example.
